  "_comment": "Russian gold-suite. Three buckets: focused smoke (one error per block), anti-FP (must return zero matches), and a large mixed paragraph that also stresses the chunker. `accept` is a list of acceptable replacements (case-sensitive); `accept_contains` matches if any candidate substring appears in any returned replacement.",
